arathotmail.com (obviously use the at sign and email me if you have any questions).He was prompt (waiting for us at the appointed time,) called us the prior day to confirm. His English was great but most importantly his attitude was awesome. He took us to a great place for Lunch after hiking the great wall for 4 hours, and then we went to the Summer Palace. I cannot recommend him enough. He is also available for city tours. The hotel is in an excellent location but was hard for me to sleep there. Also the lighting was very dim.	
